  "description": "Credibility assessment for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump. Thirteen credibility factors evaluated under ASME V&V 40-2018 at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed. Decision record documents acceptance outcome. Context of Use scope is not declared under this Minimal-profile package.",
