      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation or GCI applied on at least three systematically refined meshes with GCI below 5% on hemolysis QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study completed; GCI on hemolysis index is 8.3%, exceeding the 5% threshold; achieved level below required for Class III device at MRL 5."
